						"subtitle": "The cybersecurity landscape is constantly evolving, and traditional solutions may no longer provide the protection your organisation needs. It's time to rethink your approach.",
						"copy": "__Book our Network & Security Transformation Workshop__, where our security specialists will help you build a strategic roadmap to strengthen your defences and modernise your infrastructure.\n\n__In this interactive session, you'll:__\n- Assess your current architecture to identify gaps, pain points, and vulnerabilities\n- Develop a business case for security consolidation and network modernisation\n- Map out a seamless migration plan \n- Define your starting point with prioritised use cases and quick wins for immediate impact\n\n__Take the next step—book your personalised workshop today!__\n\n![Journey to SASE - image](//cf-assets.www.cloudflare.com/slt3lc6tev37/0SoGLk7y9ZYeAOQHh1xNo/da67cc3a60afc32cc00a36613b0c70cc/Journey_to_SASE_-_image.png)",
